assertion.value: All authors are shareholders of Illumina Inc. All authors are employees of Illumina Inc., except for GH and RTH who are former employees of Illumina Inc.

assertion.name: Ethics
assertion.value: Data analysis was completed under an institutional review board research exemption (ID Number: ICSL-001). Informed consent was not required since no human subjects were enrolled; all study samples were de-identified residual specimens left over from routine clinical care.
